contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox settlement |name = Xinbin County |native_name = 新宾县 |official_name = 新宾满族自治县 <br> Xinbin Manchu <br> Autonomous County |settlement_type = [[Autonomous county]] |image_skyline = Yongling Tomb of Qing Dynasty - 0.JPG |image_map = ChinaFushunXinbin.png |image_caption = Pavilions holding [[Bixi (tortoise)|tortoise-borne]] stelae at the Yongling Tombs |map_caption = Location in Fushun City |subdivision_type = Country |subdivision_name = [[People's Republic of China]] |subdivision_type1 = [[Province (China)|Province]] |subdivision_name1 = [[Liaoning]] |subdivision_type2 = [[Prefecture-level city]] |subdivision_name2 = [[Fushun]] |seat = [[Xinbin Town]] |seat_type = County seat |area_total_km2 = 4287 |population = |population_as_of = |population_density_km2 = auto |population_total = 310000 |pushpin_map = China Liaoning |pushpin_label = Xinbin |pushpin_label_position = right |pushpin_map_caption = Location in Liaoning |coordinates_region = CN-21 |coordinates_display = inline,title |latNS = N |latd = 41 |latm = 44 |longEW = E |longd = 125 |longm = 02 |elevation_m = 360 |timezone = [[China Standard Time|China Standard]] |utc_offset = +8 |postal_code = 113200 |postal_code_type = [[Postal code of China|Postal code]] |area_code = 0413 |website = }} '''Xinbin Manchu Autonomous County''' ({{zh|s=新宾满族自治县 |t=新賓滿族自治縣 |p=Xīnbīn Mǎnzú Zìzhìxiàn}}), or simply '''Xinbin County''' ([[Chinese Postal Map Romanisation]]: '''Sinpin'''; {{zh|s=新宾县|t=新賓縣}}), is one of the three counties under the administration of [[Fushun]] City, in the east of [[Liaoning]] Province, Northeast China. With a population of about 310,000,{{when|date=July 2012}} it covers an area of {{convert|4287|sqkm}}. ==Administrative Divisions== There are 9 [[Town (China)|towns]], 1 [[ethnic town]] and 10 [[Townships of the People's Republic of China|townships]] in the county.<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.stats.gov.cn/tjbz/cxfldm/2011/21/04/210422.html |title = 2011年统计用区划代码和城乡划分代码：新宾满族县 |publisher = National Bureau of Statistics of the People's Republic of China |language = Simplified Chinese |accessdate = 2012-07-17}}</ref> {| |valign=top| Towns: *[[Xinbin, Liaoning|Xinbin]] (新宾镇) *[[Xiayingzi]] (下营子镇) *[[Dasiping]] (大四平镇) *[[Shangjiahe]] (上夹河镇) *[[Muqi]] (木奇镇) *[[Pingdingshan, Liaoning|Pingdingshan]] (平顶山镇) *[[Yongling]] (永陵镇) *[[Weiziyu]] (苇子峪镇) *[[Nanzamu]] (南杂木镇) *[[Wangqingmen Korean Town]] (旺清门朝鲜族镇) |valign=top| Townships: *[[Xiajiahe Township]] (下夹河乡) *[[Besisiping Township]] (北四平乡) *[[Hongsheng Township]] (红升乡) *[[Hongmiaozi Township]] (红庙子乡) *[[Tangtu Township, Liaoning|Tangtu Township]] (汤图乡) *[[Chengjiao Township, Xinbin County|Chengjiao Township]] (城郊乡) *[[Xiangshuihezi Township]] (响水河子乡) *[[Xiayuan Township]] (夏园乡) *[[Yushu Township, Liaoning|Yushu Township]] (榆树乡) *[[Jiahe Township]] (嘉禾乡) |} ==References== {{reflist}} ==External links== {{County-level divisions of Liaoning}} {{Manchu autonomy in the People's Republic of China}} [[Category:Geography of Liaoning]] [[Category:Manchu autonomous counties]] {{Liaoning-geo-stub}}
